        "stories": 1,
        "text": "Come see this charming 3-bedroom, 2-full-bath home in Garfield Heights, Ohio! This home features beautiful refinished hardwood floors and a spacious two-car detached garage. Recent updates include new electrical, a brand-new furnace and A/C, fresh LVT flooring, and freshly painted interiors on both the main floor and basement. The bathroom has been upgraded with a tiled tub/shower and modern hardware, offering a clean and stylish look. The exterior has been pressure washed, and minor concrete work has been completed, giving the home great curb appeal. Whether you're a homeowner or investor, this property offers a solid mix of comfort and value-schedule your showing today!"
